      <p id="Par63">Add either 28.5âÎ¼l or 50âng of the primary PCR DNA into 2Â° PCR plate and if needed adjust volume of each well to 28.5âÎ¼l with H<sub>2</sub>O. Add 2.5âÎ¼l of 12 unique indexed primers to each well using the pattern above. Prepare the PCR master mix and divide evenly into 8 or 12 wells of a PCR tube strip. Using a multi-channel pipette add 19âÎ¼l to each well.</p>
