      <p id="Par74">- Index 1 primer (i7 equivalent) - LTR primer running toward the flow cell sequencing the LTR end index (10âcycles).</p>
      <p id="Par75">5â²- TGTAGGTTTGGCAAGCTAGC ââ3â².</p>
      <p id="Par76">- Index 2 flow cell primer (i5) - present on the flow cell, sequencing the 10âbp adapter index then 8â10âbp UMI (18â20âcycles).</p>
      <p id="Par77">- Read 2 primer - LTR primer reading the integration-genome junction.</p>
